## Create intervention


### Resource

`<%= ENV['APP_HOSTNAME'] %>/v1/interventions`


### URL parameters

Parameter | Description | Required
--------- | ----------- | --------


### Query String

Parameter | Description | Required
--------- | ----------- | --------


### HTTP request method

`POST`


### HTTP headers

<%= partial 'includes/http/headers/auth' %>


### HTTP body

{
	"intervention": {
		"type": "Intervention::Single",
		"name": "Intervention example 1",
		"body": {
			"key1": 1,
			"key2": 2
		}
	}
}


### Note
Required keys:
* `type`;
* `name`.

`type` key has to contains one of the following values:
* `Intervention::Multiple`;
* `Intervention::Single`.


> HTTP example request

```http
POST <%= ENV['APP_HOSTNAME'] %>/v1/interventions
```

```http
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
access-token: xxxyyyzzz
token-type: Bearer
client: xxxyyyzzz
uid: user@<%= ENV['DOMAIN_NAME'] %>
```

```json
{
	"intervention": {
		"type": "Intervention::Single",
		"name": "Intervention example 1",
		"body": {
			"key1": 1,
			"key2": 2
		}
	}
}
```


> HTTP response 200 OK


